    <span class="kicker">Market Comparison · Latin America</span>
    <h1>Venezuela vs. Colombia: Where to Invest in Latin America (2026)</h1>
    <p class="lead">Two neighboring economies at opposite stages — Colombia offers stability with modest returns, Venezuela offers extreme valuations with extreme risk. A data-driven comparison for investors weighing both markets.</p>
