            <tr><td>Direct FDI</td><td class="col-col">Open; equal treatment; no minimum investment</td><td class="col-ven">Possible via CPPs or reformed JVs; requires sanctions compliance; OFAC GL 49/50A for oil</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Real Estate</td><td class="col-col">Open to foreigners; strong legal framework; popular in Medellín, Bogotá, Cartagena</td><td class="col-ven">Open but complex; requires local presence, SIEX registration, CADIVI approval</td></tr>
